{"tid":1538700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你覺得已經成功爭取，唔該你入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:33:30.000Z","uid":139732,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"095fc49f784992026c4848bd26aa8373dc11aed1","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"你地好好記住以下一班手足<br />\n<br />\n熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019<br />\n<br />\n仲有爆眼手足，無數比人捉左，面臨多項控罪，比黑警打嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你點對得住佢地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UDNEsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UDNEsD.png&h=b8c253f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，記者朋友幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問下個閪婆<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">壽終正寢</span></span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤回</span></span>有咩分別?"},{"pid":"33d0712982d9ce764bc649e5092ea5c06db6b810","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e0bec3439b043fc05b12003c549d0c73243616a8","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e1653329d0736c5700cd383de1fcd4eaca39da86","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"