"tid":1538700,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cb877748fb989801a9f7d66f55acc804455da8f0","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"48e59037c9558139ad4f72a7f140429ab1ba3366","tid":1538700,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布香港人要6大訴求, 要加埋解散現役警隊及重組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533820</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"77aec35267d5e66582b78873ddef3a9a079b7395","tid":1538700,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkxOoXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkxOoXL.jpg&h=8a43af07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2615e042287332113db9d0f7f0eebbb496f3cc8","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"33367b5682450b3e233bab55bb98bf66167459e2","tid":1538700,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"尸<br />\n口<br />\n巾<br />\n我數學唔好，點解我點數佢回應訢求都係小於5"},{"pid":"17e919a86882d31e256f5a920ae3dbe2a2bf5153","tid":1538700,"uid":31166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a27baf3d9b7b1f4e3888feb984e3a881355864c","tid":1538700,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ca8e9e42e70173a719538a3924eac62f1fd5649","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7750f596ab479cf2bc42a5360ac3abfcbaac8f13","tid":1538700,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ad1aa3734fd824f58d077afe618c0cf0b3b42f4","tid":1538700,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b394e65eecec69dc0cbd2f01e625cc75b7125d","tid":1538700,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"},{"pid":"53adc63125ecf71462af2f4690a2f15849e51f08","tid":1538700,"uid":139732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}